{
  "texts": [
    "We find substantial gains using GPT-4 (CoT) and GPT-3 (CoT) over GPT-3 (Q/A).",
    "Fine-tuned GPT-3 performs the best on all subtasks, demonstrating the utility of training on our entire dataset.",
    "Note that GPT-4 doesn't support finetuning.",
    "8 Task 2: Investigating Agency in Dialogue Systems",
    "We investigate the feasibility of generating dialogues imbued with Agency and establish baseline performance of current large language models (LLMs)."
  ]
}